msgstr "Deimhnigh an tAthshocrú"

msgid ""
"Reset the system?\n"
"\n"
"This will stop all operations and return equipment to initial state."
msgstr ""
"Athshocraigh an córas?\n"
"\n"
"Stopfar gach oibríocht agus fillfidh an trealamh ar an staid thosaigh."

msgid "Confirm Calibration"
msgstr "Deimhnigh an Callú"

msgid ""
"Start calibration procedure?\n"
"\n"
"All equipment will be moved to home position.\n"
"This may take several minutes."
msgstr ""
"Tosaigh an nós imeachta callaithe?\n"
"\n"
"Cuirfear an trealamh uile chuig an suíomh baile.\n"
"D'fhéadfadh sé seo roinnt nóiméad a thógáil."

